<div class="container">
    <h2>Implicit Association Test</h2>

    <p>
        You will classify images of insects and mammals and positive
        and negative words.
    </p>

    <p>
        Use the E key for items assigned to the left and the I key
        for items assigned to the right.
    </p>

    <p>
        Select Continue to begin.
    </p>
</div>
